{"tid":2341263,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"想當年gba啱啱出嗰陣玩konami賽車，由於有大量語音，好似玩緊家用機咁","createTime":"2020-12-26T08:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T11:52:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c2927175413618f9ceff9205aa80bdda378a9d04","tid":2341263,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:04:00.000Z","msg":"坐巴士嗰陣大家爭住睇打機，依家好難有當年嘅科技大躍進，想當年，好鐘意偷睇人哋玩咩gb/gg game，依家啲電話game弱智到無興趣偷睇"},{"pid":"0084ad3306e912972748d584ed3e90e6531aa80c","tid":2341263,"uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzkJmR8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzkJmR8.jpg&h=e2b84d70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb06029a1c92c69f8901ab896c9152623b12f7c4","tid":2341263,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"【#LikeJapan遊戲動漫】28年前的聖誕遊戲大特賣 有多少東西曾經是你的收藏？<br />\n聖誕節最好當然就是買部遊戲機送給人或是獎勵一下自己(當然前題是有機&hellip;&hellip;)，有網友就分享一張28年前的聖誕任天堂遊戲大特賣宣傳單張，當年超級任天堂推出了大約2年，PS、SS甚至曇花一現的3DO都還沒有推出。不知當年大家又正在玩哪些遊戲呢？<br />\n<br />\nby #Likejapan_阿FA<br />\n鳴謝圖片授權：PICORHYTHM（ぴこりずむ）@picopy303<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/picopy303/status/1324187695208280064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpicopy303%2Fstatus%2F1324187695208280064&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=a3f5ba3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpicopy303%2Fstatus%2F1324187695208280064&h=406abcc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/picopy303/status/1324187695208280064</a><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n「你眼中的新潟・東北魅力是？」有獎問卷調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://rebrand.ly/LJniigatasurveyBT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frebrand.ly%2FLJniigatasurveyBT&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUi%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=c63698d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rebrand.ly/L